Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.68,0:01:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兼續
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.16,0:01:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼她會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.66,0:01:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.61,0:01:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 這個人是在海邊被怪物吞到肚子裡的大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.49,0:01:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 你現在才認出來啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.15,0:01:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.51,0:01:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為你突然溜了 在這幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.33,0:01:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了一大跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.71,0:02:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛之戰士 直江兼續從今日起以此為據點…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.46,0:02:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼哥哥要你襲擊宗朗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.43,0:02:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼哥哥會操縱那個式神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.53,0:02:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥到底知道我們這邊多少事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點給千從實招來!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.54,0:02:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不過是個小嘍羅而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是什麼小嘍羅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.86,0:02:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟你什麼都不知道的樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.15,0:02:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果被指派的任務也失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小嘍羅中的小嘍羅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.53,0:02:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對啦 才不是小嘍羅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人應該是棄子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你居然還懂這種詞…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.07,0:02:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天小幸說的 說兼續是一個笨蛋棄子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我既不是笨蛋也不是棄子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我拋棄了德川慶彥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點可不許你們搞錯了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來還是個正宗的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 從今天起我要在這裡監視色情魔柳生宗朗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 難道你要住在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用問
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.28,0:03:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我反對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能讓這麼危險的人物待在公主大人的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾身能理解你擔憂主公的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.71,0:03:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但兼續所說的應該屬實
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最討厭撒謊和水母了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這傢伙就是個笨蛋嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒這麼高技術會撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可公主大人要是有個三長兩短…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千現在可是劍姬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.87,0:03:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒有半藏在身邊 也能保護好自己啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.22,0:03:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.31,0:03:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一出事了 我會保護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 求求你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵衛會好好照顧她的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正這傢伙也沒任務了 至少能當個看門狗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.73,0:03:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我當狗看待是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵衛會好好餵她飯吃 帶她去散步的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.79,0:04:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 小續續
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs23}(*十兵衛將兼續名字中的「続(つぐ)」倒過來唸兩遍變成「ぐつぐつ」意為咕嘟咕嘟)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小續續?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 跟煮火鍋的聲音一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小續續的外號喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.11,0:04:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為直江續續唸起來好拗口耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.79,0:04:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪個都不對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是兼!續!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 玩笑話就到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.65,0:04:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入正題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個數據你都解析完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.42,0:04:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 以妾身的能力根本輕而易舉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過有點睡眠不足就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些在哥哥的文件夾裡的?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.78,0:04:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜都只是一些片段
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從別墅的服務器上拷貝的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部份的文件都被破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後只修復出來這些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天魔…連其名都為人忌諱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:04:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 德川慶彥肯定在圖謀不軌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這之中最難以理解的 就是這段音頻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Quoniam impletum est tempus,et appropinquavit regnum Dei: poenitemini,et credite Evangelio
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這令人發寒的聲音 到底是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶彥大人的聲音…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.74,0:05:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 這不是哥哥的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵衛?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽過…這個聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 十兵衛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪兒聽到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是誰的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs23}覺醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs23}汝之主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵衛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵衛 振作一點!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧 十兵衛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.80,0:05:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是誰的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.81,0:05:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:06:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有搞錯啊 還來這麼老掉牙的暈倒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼你還在那兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.20,0:06:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大發慈悲地來幫你們解讀也不是不可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂這段話的意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 不瞞你說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人直江兼續 可是有英檢4級證書喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs23}(*全名為「實用英語技能檢定」 共分為7個等級 最低為5級)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英檢4級…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得這是上國中時必須通過的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.10,0:06:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小續續好厲害 居然會英文
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你終於明白我有多麼偉大了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.23,0:06:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是拉丁語
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.38,0:06:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段音頻數據的發音很像拉丁語
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉…拉丁語?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪國語言?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還被加密了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假設這段音頻是拉丁語的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用發音最接近的拉丁語置換
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再翻譯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「日期滿了 神的國近了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們當悔改 信福音」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs23}(*此段取自馬可福音1：15)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.03,0:07:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是被禁的異教福音書中記載的一節
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被禁的福音書?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這種東西會出現在慶彥大人的數據裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾身也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.28,0:07:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 外面還晾著衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是千的和服淋濕了有你好看的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.21,0:07:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.84,0:07:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜點!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小續續沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋沒這麼容易死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 我們繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來應該會清靜一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.02,0:07:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 宗朗你也別管那些啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 好不容易才補好的墻…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:07:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那可是我的小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的很煩誒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.86,0:08:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千姬也一起來睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑什麼千得在這個狗屋裡睡覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到這之後 公主大人真的變了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那個時候判若兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來 第一次見到公主大人的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也下著雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在這裡的是這次轉學到武應學園的德川千公主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,0:08:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天起 你將奉命做千姬大人的貼身護衛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.67,0:08:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後一定要寸步不離地保護千姬大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵…遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半藏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在擔任千姬大人貼身護衛的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想給你一個重大的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.66,0:08:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能成為千姬大人的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千姬大人的…同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半藏 你與千姬大人同齡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定能成為她真正的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對此堅信不移
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.22,0:09:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做…千姬大人真正的好朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到沒 轉學來的將軍家的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.33,0:09:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微瞅了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和傳言說的一樣 真不招人喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 反正別跟她扯上關係就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是德川家公主的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得 有話應該當面說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不應該…躲在別人背後說這種話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你心裡肯定也是這麼想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.69,0:09:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我才沒有想過…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低年級的囂張個鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.94,0:09:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 就你這樣子還去保護公主大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是敢告狀有你好看的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 諒她也沒那個膽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:10:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一刻 我在心裡發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.27,0:10:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要變強
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時時刻刻 寸步不離
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來親手保護千姬大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在 千姬大人已經交到了這麼多的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我的使命已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起洗吧 半藏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 呃 十兵衛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是個好日子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.09,0:10:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小續續來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後會更加更加歡樂的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會覺得寂寞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.37,0:10:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想過要和宗朗兩人獨處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:10:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想是想過啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.82,0:11:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是十兵衛呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.40,0:11:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡和大家一起!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.80,0:11:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家在一起可以看到各種反應的哥哥 我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是值得高興的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼～熱乎乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵衛!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰 快點出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然攻擊十兵衛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不會輕易放過你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.00,0:11:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算躲起來我也能立刻找到你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半藏 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.26,0:11:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗朗 有敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵衛被襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.69,0:11:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 十兵衛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷勢如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是失去意識了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人呢 到底在哪裡 半藏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 但是真的來過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不見的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不見的敵人?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又兵衛!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.22,0:12:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔斷壁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.78,0:12:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙小人 不要躲躲藏藏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸村 又兵衛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.01,0:12:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又兵衛!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是昏過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點到結界裡面來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.89,0:12:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵衛也被攻擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有外傷 但昏迷不醒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.43,0:12:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕被敵人的妖術催眠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸村 你…受傷了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為睡眠不足一時大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算還能把結界撐起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.28,0:12:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不知道能維持多久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半藏 敵人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才起一直在找 但這裡沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.68,0:12:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前說她先去睡了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 一個人去太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.69,0:13:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半藏 那個到底是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…只知道是看不見的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不見的敵人?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.97,0:13:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.89,0:13:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏那個時候躲開了手裏劍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.47,0:13:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我能看到它們 以我的速度根本…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒受傷吧 半藏 千姬大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗朗 其他人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.69,0:13:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被突然襲擊 都受了傷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在都躲在幸村的結界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.47,0:13:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但恐怕撐不了很久…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只要在這裡幹掉那些傢伙就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,典雅流麗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.61,0:13:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半藏 看見敵人後立刻告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何不讓千姬大人戴上那個眼鏡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.87,0:14:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的 那個眼鏡是為半藏量身打造的特訂品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有股熱反應在接近廚房
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷皇閃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.74,0:14:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.22,0:14:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是 不想活了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.85,0:14:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是…我只是想來說你們吵到我睡覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人 快離她遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.28,0:14:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定她就是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.34,0:14:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在懷疑她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.23,0:14:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了 話說你懷疑什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種傢伙怎麼可能會是幕後黑手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.47,0:14:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在背後 公主大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兼續 沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷皇閃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉它了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.43,0:15:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 危險
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 到院子裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是敵人剛剛逃出去的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個主意 相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.51,0:15:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 宗朗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也等等我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當真要主動接近敵人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才有一瞬間 我看到了那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為淋到雨所以敵人顯露出身形來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.73,0:15:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 只要看得見 我們就贏定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 發現敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.34,0:15:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉開安全的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在等雨停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦雨停了我們就沒有勝算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且幸村她們的結界也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨好像快停了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.29,0:15:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半藏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.36,0:15:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和宗朗接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.49,0:15:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在這種時候做如此下流之事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.41,0:15:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等雨停了 就只有你能看見那個敵人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打敗那傢伙 只能讓半藏成為劍姬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來接吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為劍姬的話 就能保護公主大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間猶豫了 快點和宗朗接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁我現在還看得見那個敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半藏 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果…果然還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.36,0:16:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 宗朗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.68,0:16:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的將相只有公主大人一個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.05,0:16:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼啊笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.97,0:16:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都這種時候還糾結這些無聊的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.39,0:16:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這麼磨蹭下去敵人就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:16:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 雨停了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗朗 危險
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗朗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.74,0:17:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My cottage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很礙事耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人 那傢伙已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗朗 宗朗 醒醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 接吻機器死翹翹了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是昏過去而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.59,0:17:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再胡說八道 我一刀殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗朗 求求你 快醒過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.41,0:17:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗朗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.70,0:17:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 這下你成不了劍姬了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.02,0:17:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須得想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 那一天 我在心裡發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要變強
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論發生什麼事 都要保護公主大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.68,0:17:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護好千姬大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潛藏在暗處的愚蠢之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決不允許你繼續在千姬大人的面前肆意妄為
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半藏 你這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要賭上性命 消滅你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快退下 半藏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.96,0:18:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能離開我太遠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人 我在這裡制止住那些傢伙的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.85,0:18:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你一定要消滅他們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋鐵鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.43,0:18:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們上鉤了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒法攻擊你們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少我…能封住你們的行動!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半藏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.94,0:18:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把敵人和我一起砍掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼蠢話 我怎麼可能下得了手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是千的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:19:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您已經不再需要…我這個貼身護衛了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半藏…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你…公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.78,0:19:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快沒時間了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.93,0:19:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兼續 幫我一個忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.99,0:19:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難 難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.49,0:19:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半藏我…半藏我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠侍奉您…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.00,0:19:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是三生有幸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兼續 就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看見了 電皇石火
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半藏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半藏 振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.14,0:19:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.32,0:20:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子都不知道誰是誰的護衛了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.75,0:20:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級大笨蛋!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.42,0:20:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於千來說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.49,0:20:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可不是什麼無足輕重的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從十年前的那一天起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是半藏不在了 千…要怎麼才好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來救千?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.34,0:20:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來袒護千?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.64,0:20:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來…做千的好朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.02,0:20:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你下次再做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千死也不會饒你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.76,0:20:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.53,0:20:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 那兩個人到底什麼關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.02,0:20:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將與士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也是最要好的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.34,0:20:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 居然活過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是妖術解除了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:20:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧她們兩個打倒了敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:20:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是三個人好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是有我大力相助怎麼可能贏得了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.06,0:21:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.88,0:21:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵衛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.93,0:21:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸村 又兵衛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.73,0:21:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 十兵衛的小狗屋不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No! 是I am my cottage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.73,0:21:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 真的會說英文耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.98,0:21:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…句子都錯了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.56,0:21:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! We can!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.88,0:21:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來很感人的一個場面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就不能安靜點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.10,0:21:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半藏 幹掉她們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.36,0:21:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 可是我受傷了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.28,0:21:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你敢不聽千的命令嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.91,0:21:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百花繚亂 SAMURAI GIRLS
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.99,0:21:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.49,0:21:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籠罩大日本的暗影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.91,0:23:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半藏的眼鏡有多少功能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概有300個左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.78,0:23:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼多!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.30,0:23:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望遠鏡 熱反應感應器 夜視功能自是不在話下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.57,0:23:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還可以查找數據 檢測對方的戰鬥力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.92,0:23:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外內置數碼相機和GPS
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.99,0:23:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還可以隔離99%的紫外線
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.49,0:23:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過肯定很貴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.74,0:23:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實連運費只要19800日元喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.92,0:23:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手續費由德川家承擔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.25,0:23:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵衛也想要一個!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.38,0:23:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 百花繚亂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.95,0:23:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠之奴隸
